<title>CHILDREN MAY BE HERALDS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Naupang neu haw hukdamna lopi gente hi thei ui,
 I Tanpau leh Kross A put chuh a genviel thei ui;
 Gamla taka umte chuh lungmuonna neihsak dingin,
 A Pathienni thilpiek un Bible a thak thei ui.

[V2]
 Naupang neu haw Hukdampa hehpihna kipah-
 Um gente ahi thei ui;
 Naupang neuhaw'n Pathien thu genin mi tamtak
 Van In chuh a hilh thei ui.

[V3]
 2. Naupang neuhaw'n Lalpa nasep ah hihding a nei ui,
 Lungkhamna leh buoina meipi a hihmang thei ui;
 Lunggil ngui leh hatlo lungkhama taute kawm achun,
 Ni vak hawihtak guolin thu nemtak a gen thei ui.

[V4]
 3. Hukdampa thutiem achun naupante hetzing a hiu,
 Hehpih tatna vangsakna chu le a chang thei ui;
 Amau haw chuh zainem takin a veng zinga, vana,
 A vansawlchak-teuin Pa mel a mu zing sek ui.</lyrics>
</song>